<h5 id="head-74437420da36ec142156a02314d70914607cd67c">Mirkwood 12:</h5>
<strong>FF / 18 Cold Vortices.</strong> I can handle that. My pack is full, though, so I recall out of Mirkwood (up to Wilderness level) and overland back to- <h5 id="head-1df3a221d576f88a753eb802683fa2569bac1c8c">Lothlorien:</h5>

    <ul>

    <li>
<p>
 Neither junkart can be sold, so I *ID* them. Here's a twist: They both activate for remove fear and cure poison every 5 turns. I keep the Dagger and drop the other in the trees. 
</p>
