Of course, this means I now *have* to go Overland, as I bought every CCW in Lothlorien before going down the last time. Very grumpily, I head to Minas Anor for the first time. <h5 id="head-d07f712a94847165a1a0ff5c147f07442eac34a2">Minas Anor:</h5>
There is zilch here except for 8 CCWs, a staff of sense hidden, and a quest I receive that I'm not going to be doing any time soon. On my way back to Lothlorien, I receive my first fate. <h5 id="head-1df3a221d576f88a753eb802683fa2569bac1c8c-7">Lothlorien:</h5>

