 Now I have a problem. I know where I have to go to get out - magic mapping makes that clear - but I can NOT make that dumb door appear! Digging is not working - 'You fail to make even the slightest of progress.' My piety is slowly creeping downward as I search at it (it was around -2000 for a while there, darn it.) I change my exploration to slug-like (giving me 'excellent' searching) and try again. No luck. 
