 My goodness, I got them all. (I was going to count for you, but there were WAY too many.) I peek out, then read a scroll of light I found. Well, ok, there's a little Grey Mold over there in the corner, minding its own business. I let it alone. Moving along, I run into a pack of Gnome Mages. I kill some, the others scatter. In the spoil I find a Wand of Dig. Did I mention the RNG hates me?!? I also find a Staff of Remove Curses, which I use, and another of Identify. A scroll of enchant to-dam successfully enchants my crossbow up another point. 
