 So where is Azog? I start exploring, and get close to that last place with all the wererats/etc is. I see an odd sight: wall sections disappearing, some distance away from me in that same wererat room. (I don't think I have telepathy or whatever...weird.) 'There is a grinding sound.' A pair of rock moles. 
