 Current visible monster list is 11 wolves, 12 black orcs, 8 forest trolls, a pair of blink dogs, 16 uruks, the ranger, Gorbag and Azog. I get a clear shot and shoot the ranger. (I have a screen shot of around now, too.) 180/257 hp. I wish I hadn't dumped those potions of speed back in my house, but to be fair, those hounds would probably have shattered them all. 
