 Gorbag starts hitting me. Well, actually, trying to. He's missing consistently. I quaff a few CCW (other attacks are landing, mostly arrows from the uruks) and my one potion of invisibility. I fight my way down towards a corridor, and reach it, with 149/257. It's a darned good thing I had so many CCW - the hounds and some traps broke a bunch of them, I've quaffed many, and I have 33 left. 
