<h5 id="head-1df3a221d576f88a753eb802683fa2569bac1c8c-8">Lothlorien:</h5>

    <ul>

    <li>
<p>
 Whew, I'm glad that's over with! I ID the last few things in my pack, and come up with a Shocking Metal Boomerang (3d4) (+5,+6). I sell quite a bit, though I'm hanging on to the Deathwatch artifacts since the weaponsmith at Lorien caps at 10k. 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
