First, I think I'll going to grab that FF quest I know is waiting in Mirkwood. Then, I don't know. Probably the Old Forest (being careful of that Death Fate) or the Maze. Lothlorien Old Mages &amp; Lothlorien spider quests. And maybe some more Angband dragon scumming tossed in Possibly even REAL Angband scumming, assuming I'm allowed down the stairs... I need *good* rings/amulets. But not til I get rpoison I may be silly, but I'm not insane. 
