 Somewhat smaller level than normal. Some wandering shows probable cause of the feeling: a checkerboard pit. Contents: Stargazer, Green dragon fly, Dark hounds, Clear hounds, and assorted others. Dark hounds blind me, and I tree walk outside to heal up, then go back. Cake, and I net an Oil of Eagle. This really doesn't warrant an {excellent}, so I keep going. Some time later I find the true source: an Orc Pit, and right next to it a small room filled with novice rangers, and one Black Louse. 
