 I head first for the Black louse - it's amidst the rangers. A Gold Firebird shows up and is quickly killed by a ranger. (That seems wrong, doesn't it? ) Even though I shift to 'running', the dang louse gets away from me -- it was too far away to start with and started multiplying in the trees. There's no way short of geno that I could get them all now, and I don't have geno. Blast. I turn around and dive into the orcs. (After I kill about 10, I remember to start praying again ) 
</p>
