<h5 id="head-49120aec13103902bddc5e8db90305c4ff949aed">Old Forest 22 / excellent:</h5>
Right next to me, a Jelly Pit. I explore a little, kill a bunch of gnome mages (Pt, fwiw), and- <h5 id="head-520e6d78681ea1a5c7324e10311103ee86c18e8b">Old Forest 23 / very good:</h5>

