<p>
 Well, I didn't see the quest entrance on the way, but I didn't really explore for it either. 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 BM has a Mattock of Digging (+6), but I leave it be. I've got Thrain, and a Magical Mattock (or some such) will show up eventually. 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 I find three, count'em, CCWs. Ugh. It's night, so I nap at the inn. Day brings 7 more, but that makes only 30, and I want more. I guess I get to go to Bree after all. 
</p>
</li>
    <li>
<p>
 On the way out, I recheck the BM &amp; find Potions of INT and Resistance. I buy both. The Potion of INT gives me 18/85, and 8 more spell points. 
</p>
